</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/zpkZDxxt758" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/30/avervision-m5-usb-overhead-projector/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=avervision-m5-usb-overhead-projector</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>東北停電電子支付停用，當地市民：提款機也停 + 衣食住行無電不行</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/C1os_HIg-js/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 30 Sep 2021 08:40:54 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[東北停電]]></category><category><![CDATA[電子支付]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1063453</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>中國東北近日大規模停電，嚴重影響當地居民日常生活。需知道近年中國大力發展電子支付，微信支付、支付寶等工具大行其 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>中國東北近日大規模停電，嚴重影響當地居民日常生活。需知道近年中國大力發展電子支付，微信支付、支付寶等工具大行其道，已成為人民生活必需品，甚至有人認為可廢除實體貨幣。但一場大停電令民眾重新思考實體貨幣的價值。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1063464 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/YbGZXczmg3-cx8H4o0gRIu83r-uUIsFBEtjnMhLY5zI-1-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/YbGZXczmg3-cx8H4o0gRIu83r-uUIsFBEtjnMhLY5zI-1-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/YbGZXczmg3-cx8H4o0gRIu83r-uUIsFBEtjnMhLY5zI-1-1200x900.jpeg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/YbGZXczmg3-cx8H4o0gRIu83r-uUIsFBEtjnMhLY5zI-1-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/YbGZXczmg3-cx8H4o0gRIu83r-uUIsFBEtjnMhLY5zI-1-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/YbGZXczmg3-cx8H4o0gRIu83r-uUIsFBEtjnMhLY5zI-1.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲資料來源：野野野 max 微博</p><p>據自由亞洲電台報道，居住在北京的吉林人宋鵬春表示，手機和電腦均無法啟動，根本無法聯繫親友，發信息亦無人回覆。宋鵬春認為更重要的，是電子支付問題。社會大多數人都倚靠電子支付買賣，現在停電，不能使用電子支付，更不能在提款。在日常生活離不開電力的情況下，好可能出現治安問題，社會將會面臨動盪不安。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1063459 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/tVWIHwCw7dqo6H8IfncU4dcbbhzsV7pp4bg1FuG4NRY-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/tVWIHwCw7dqo6H8IfncU4dcbbhzsV7pp4bg1FuG4NRY-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/tVWIHwCw7dqo6H8IfncU4dcbbhzsV7pp4bg1FuG4NRY-1200x900.jpeg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/tVWIHwCw7dqo6H8IfncU4dcbbhzsV7pp4bg1FuG4NRY-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/tVWIHwCw7dqo6H8IfncU4dcbbhzsV7pp4bg1FuG4NRY-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/tVWIHwCw7dqo6H8IfncU4dcbbhzsV7pp4bg1FuG4NRY.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲資料來源：野野野 max 微博</p><p>人民網於日前發布一篇名為《多地拉閘限電，不能讓老百姓生活受限》的快評，指令各地政府應妥善處理停電問題，更表示「如果居民用電沒保障，會出事的」，但看來電子支付問題嚴峻，當局如無對策，恐釀成大禍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1063454 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-30-at-3.59.39-PM-540x580.png" alt="" width="540" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-30-at-3.59.39-PM-540x580.png 540w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-30-at-3.59.39-PM-839x900.png 839w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-30-at-3.59.39-PM-768x824.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-30-at-3.59.39-PM-1431x1536.png 1431w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screenshot-2021-09-30-at-3.59.39-PM.png 1491w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 540px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲人民網快評</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/electricity-09282021063026.html">自由亞洲電台</a></p><p>&#8212;</p>
